---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — LeadFair"
  description="LeadFair's privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-light text-sm mb-12">Last updated: February 17, 2026</p>

      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>LeadFair ("we," "us," "our") is a business technology company based in Huntsville, Alabama. We provide AI-powered tools and services to help small businesses grow. This policy explains how we handle your information when you use our website (leadfair.ai) and services.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you fill out a form on our website, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Phone number</li>
        <li>Business name</li>
        <li>Any additional information you provide in form fields</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We also collect standard website usage data (pages visited, browser type, etc.) through our hosting provider.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
        <li>Provide the services you request</li>
        <li>Send you text messages if you have opted in</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2>Text Messaging (SMS)</h2>
      <p>If you opt in to receive text messages from LeadFair:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>We will send messages related to your inquiry and our services</li>
        <li>Message frequency varies</li>
        <li>Message and data rates may apply</li>
        <li>You can opt out at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message</li>
        <li>Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for assistance</li>
        <li>Your phone number will not be shared with third parties for their marketing purposes</li>
        <li>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services to operate our business:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Twilio</strong> — for text messaging and phone services</li>
        <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — for website hosting</li>
        <li><strong>FormSubmit</strong> — for processing contact form submissions</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Each of these services has their own privacy policies governing how they handle data.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You can request to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>See what personal information we have about you</li>
        <li>Update or correct your information</li>
        <li>Delete your information</li>
        <li>Opt out of text messages (reply STOP)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or your data, contact us at:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: hello@leadfair.ai</li>
        <li>Website: <a href="/contact">leadfair.ai/contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
